This project offers DebugDraw for Box2D using DragronFireSDK.

IF YOU ARE USING BOX2D VERSION 2.1.2 (most are):
Add V212 to your preprocessor definitions otherwise this will not work.  If you are running the lastest version of Box2D you don't have to do anything.

Files required for DebugDraw:
Render.h
Render.cpp

Example files using DebugDraw:
App.cpp
Bodies.h
Bodies.cpp
